Guo Meimei responds to death rumor
2013-05-07 08:56:28 GMT
Guo Meimei, the "bratty rich 20-year-old mini-blogger" whose online wealth-flaunting caused a massive scandal for the Chinese Red Cross in 2011, rebutted her death rumor via Sina Weibo, an equivalent of twitter.She updated her Weibo late Monday after a break of more than one month. Online postings claimed she was murdered in Macau.As of Tuesday afernoon, her message has been retweeted more than 13,000 times by microbloggers. Comments reading "RIP" flooded her Weibo page in the past couple of days.
